snippet.title: Amber Heard Slammed For 'Disrespectful' Outfit She Wore To Mosque
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Slammed For 'Disrespectful' Outfit She Wore To Mosque
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

Amber Heard is facing backlash online, but this time it has nothing to do with johnny depp. The backlash is over an outfit she wore to an Istanbul mosque, which some people are saying was disrespectful.  Amber heard shared a series of photos to social media that showed her hair poking out, her chest and neck showing. Other people criticized her for not wearing a bra, and only wearing a headscarf as a fashion accessory. We're going to tell you all the details, right now on IO.
